original_title: Fifth Session of the Ninth Parliament to commence today
original_body_lines: COLOMBO (News 1st); The Fifth Session of the Ninth Parliament will commence today in the presence of President Ranil Wickremesinghe.
Deputy Speaker Ajith Rajapakse says the President is scheduled to present the government's policy statement at 10.30 am.
The President last adjourned the Parliament on the 26th of January.
